title.narrative: Procurement of Supplies and Logistics support - INACTIVE DO NOT USE

description.narrative: This activity (Procurement of Supplies and Logistics support - INACTIVE DO NOT USE) is a component of Sierra Leone Kerry Town Ebola Treatment Facility reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Humanitarian assistance' and a budget of £17,281,785. This component benefits Sierra Leone, and works in the following sector(s): Material relief assistance and services . , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited. The start date is 08-09-2014 and the end date is 31-08-2015.
